Package owlSpeak.engine.his

This package provides all classes for extending the dialogue control to the hidden information state approach.

See: Description

    The Field class represents a field (or slot) which can be addressed during the dialogue, e.g., in a flight booking dialogue it may be "origin" or "destination".
